message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this amazing product! I think you'll really love it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $120.
Thanks for the offer, Alice! I'm interested, but $120 is a bit higher than I was hoping to spend. Would you be willing to come down to $100?
I understand you're looking to save some money, Bob! I can see if I can do a bit better. How about $110? It's a great compromise between our initial offer and your counteroffer.
